    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5615836/" class="title-link">关于喜欢什么和内心平静</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5615836"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/sysysysy/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u3146470-8.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sysysysy/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">吧唧吧唧</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-10-13"
      class="main-meta">2012-10-13 18:13:03</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5615836_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  哲理警句什么的，有点像以前在日本吃的那个猪鼻子甜点。都说很好吃，确实很好吃，然后吃吃吃。但是塞太多了又觉得不过如此（结果只买回国两盒，万分残念）——却在之后的九年岁月里，每次吃甜点的时候，都会不停地想起它。  学姐谈创业，说创意最廉价。其实世间的道理也是呀，...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5615836/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">5有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
